title: ELECTROMAGNETIC FLOW METER IOT GATEWAY (TELEMETRY SYSTEM)
description:
iot module (telemetry system) 
 
key parameters as below : 
 
rs485 iot gateway gprs module . 
 
 1.store three-month data recorded on cloud , 
 
2.you can download data record in pdf format direct from website. 
 
3.login id & password provided in each module 
 
4.maximum 3 nos rs485 input connect on single module. 
 
5.sim card scope of user ( airtel, vodafone ,idea, bsnl ) note : jio sim card not allowed 
 
6.supply voltage required 24 v dc for gsm module. note : arrange by user 
 
7.rail mount module . 
 
8.onine you can see and store data like flow rate , total flow ,velocity on each 15 min interval period . 
 
9.ones in a day 1 sms received in register mobile no. you can add more then one mobile no. 
 
10.when you send massage from register mobile no ' status' you can receive current time flow rate ,total reading on your mobile via sms .
